Returned compatibility edition min version to Gingerbread

The LampShade core (Groups, Moods, and
DeviceManager/MoodPlayer/ConnectivityService) will continue to be
backwards compatible, but additional features such as Alarms, Tasker,
NFC will be only available for Honeycomb MR1 and up when possible or
IceCreamSandwitch if needed. However, existing Gingerbread devices
through Google Play may have paid for the Alarms feature, so those
devices cannot be updated to LampShade 3.0 and loose this feature
